title: 47. In Mind - Real Estate
text: Seems like it will be a good album. It's Real! by Littlemau909 Real Estate is definetly one of my top favorites, their music always cheers me up can't wait for to hear the rest of this amazing album. Biography Formed: 2009 in Ridgewood, NJ Genre: Alternative Years Active: '00s, '10s New Jersey's Real Estate stake their claim to a warm, hazy style of indie rock with breezy melodies. The band was formed in Ridgewood by lead singer/guitarist Martin Courtney (Predator Vision and formerly Titus Andronicus), guitarist Matthew Mondanile (Ducktails), bassist Alex Bleeker (Alex Bleeker & the Freaks), and drummer Etienne Duguay (Predator Vision).
